column5: Dear Lady Quinte, Although you were a freezing bugger this morning you always redeem yourself and hook me up with beautiful fish.  Only 2 for the day 5.11/6.5 both on RR. 200 back 100 out, 40-50 ft water.
big head on the left, small head on the right.  Eerie is a deary! Nice catch
Great catch.About time she started giving out some nice ones
Cold hard gold....better than sittin' on the couch I'd say
Thanks for sharing  David  aka  Superdad
No problem David and thanks for you updates and tips over the last couple years. It's guys like you that are a big help on this board.  Mark
